OL,4,CRegulator warns against use of Peloton
OL,5,Ctreadmill
OL,6, Safety regulators in the US have urged
OL,7, owners of a Peloton treadmill to stop
OL,8, using the product "immediately" if they
OL,9, have children or pets in the home.
OL,11,FThe Consumer Product Safety Commission
OL,12,F(CPSC) says it is aware of 39 incidents
OL,13,Fincluding one death, involving the
OL,14,FPeloton Tread+.
OL,16,FPeloton had already confirmed the death
OL,17,Flast month and said children should
OL,18,Fstay away from the machines.
OL,20,FOn Saturday, Peloton called the CPSC's
OL,21,Fwarning "inaccurate and misleading".
